{
  "_notes": "Configured June 2026. AAP runs the SearchSpring Snap theme (ul.ss__results, .ss__pagination__*). Category taxonomy: /fire-rated/, /flush/, /recessed/, etc. (no /products/ umbrella). No pro-club form (/pro-club-application/ 404s). No subcategory boxes on any category page (subcategoryBox: null). Qty stepper buttons absent (no data-action inc/dec; bare .form-increment input). Related carousel is SS recommendation (.ss__recommendation--carousel). Footer: bare <footer> with .box h3 headings, div.copyright for copyright text; phone in footer-bottom-col (1 tel: link). Mobile nav is #mySidenav. LIGHTHOUSE (calibrated July 2 2026, live scores homepage a11y 66 / plp 73 / pdp 64): theme structurally below a healthy a11y score, but clears the fleet-wide accessibility:60 floor (no per-store override). Partly tied to the known sub-44px touch-target deficiency: when the AAP dev CSS fix ships, re-measure and raise these floors.",
  "_absentFeatures": [
    {
      "configKey": "forms.proClub",
      "fillWith": "{ \"path\": \"/<form-page>/\", \"submitUrlPattern\": \"**/forms.zohopublic.com/**/<ZohoFormName>/**/submit\" }",
      "verifiedAbsent": "/pro-club-application/ returns 404 (verified June 2026)",
      "enables": "pro-club-form.cy.js"
    },
    {
      "configKey": "forms.becomeVendor",
      "fillWith": "{ \"path\": \"/<form-page>/\", \"submitUrlPattern\": \"**/forms.zohopublic.com/**/<ZohoFormName>/**/submit\" }",
      "verifiedAbsent": "no become-a-vendor page on live site (June 2026 onboarding)",
      "enables": "become-vendor-form.cy.js"
    },
    {
      "configKey": "forms.architectInquiries",
      "fillWith": "{ \"path\": \"/<form-page>/\", \"submitUrlPattern\": \"**/forms.zohopublic.com/**/<ZohoFormName>/**/submit\" }",
      "verifiedAbsent": "no /architects/ page on live site (June 2026 onboarding)",
      "enables": "architect-form.cy.js"
    },
    {
      "configKey": "plp.subcategory",
      "fillWith": "\"/<parent-category>/<child-category>/\"",
      "verifiedAbsent": "flat category taxonomy - no child categories exist (June 2026 onboarding)",
      "enables": "plp.cy.js subcategory suite"
    }
  ],
